overning the micro and macro components. We\npresent numerical results that demonstrate the performance of the mM method.\nThe mM method is also compared against a corresponding DG-IMEX method solving\ndirectly for $f$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jul 2021 16:53:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-11"}
