d robustness than existing single and\nensemble ML models, demonstrating the state-of-the-art certified L2-robustness\non MNIST, CIFAR-10, and ImageNet datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jul 2021 18:10:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2022 04:14:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-22"}
