d approach performs on par or better,\nconfirming the suitability of the developed shape prior and probabilistic model\nfor vehicle reconstruction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jul 2021 19:47:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-09"}
