tion of mirror modes at Mars from the joint\npoints of view of magnetic field, electron and ion measurements. Up until now,\nthe lack of high-temporal resolution plasma measurements has prevented such an\nin-depth study.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jul 2021 13:34:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Feb 2022 13:44:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
